# Code Review Checklist

## Spec & Architecture

- [ ] Matches relevant `docs/feature-specs/` entry
- [ ] Respects module boundaries (NestJS domain modules, R3F scene folders)
- [ ] Uses `@ultron/shared` types — no duplicated enums or WS event shapes
- [ ] REST/WS changes reflected in `docs/architecture/api-contracts.md`
- [ ] Numeric values match `docs/canonical-numbers.md`
- [ ] New patterns have an ADR if architectural

## TypeScript & Quality

- [ ] Strict mode compliant; no unjustified `any` or `@ts-ignore`
- [ ] Exported functions have explicit return types
- [ ] Error handling on all API endpoints and async client flows
- [ ] Input validation on all external inputs (DTOs / Zod)
- [ ] Soft deletes respected in database queries

## Frontend

- [ ] Canvas loaded with `ssr: false`; single Canvas maintained
- [ ] Zustand narrow selectors; correct store ownership
- [ ] Tailwind + design tokens; accessible 2D alternatives for 3D actions
- [ ] LOD applied before high-detail geometry

## Backend

- [ ] Versioned under `/api/v1/`
- [ ] No blocking LLM calls in controllers — queued via Bull
- [ ] Redis/WS channel names match contracts
- [ ] Prometheus metrics for new endpoints
- [ ] No N+1 queries; indexes used

## Security

- [ ] No secrets in code or logs
- [ ] No user input in paths, shell, or dynamic imports
- [ ] Output escaped where rendered in HTML
- [ ] Rate limiting on new public endpoints

## Performance

- [ ] Scene code-split by scale; assets instanced where specified
- [ ] WS updates throttled/batched appropriately
- [ ] No per-frame React state updates in 3D loop

## Tests & Docs

- [ ] Tests cover new business logic and validation
- [ ] Feature spec / memory docs updated if behavior changed
- [ ] Technical debt flagged in `docs/memory/technical-debt.md` if deferred
